data.description: This one is NOT a drive-by! Spacious 3 bedroom 2 full bath ranch with garage and fully fenced yard. One floor living at it's best! Upon entering the home, you'll be impressed with the size of your living room and it's Bamboo wood flooring, ceiling fan, recessed lighting and Bose surround sound.  Bring  on the furniture! You can enter your kitchen with full appliance package, double sink, counter seating for 4 and loads of cabinets through the first opening. 2nd opening brings you to your dining room with sliding doors to your back patio. Large laundry room with wet sink and 2nd door to the backyard. Bring your dog as there's a doggie door for convenience. Primary bedroom ensuite with newer tiled stall shower awaits. Bedrooms two and three are good size with generous closets. Storage not a problem with the pull down stairs to attic. Your back yard has wood fencing, storage shed and large shed with electric. Tankless hot water and Solar panels that are owned make for an efficient home.  Enjoy a walk to the Lake, basketball court and new playground. Selling AS-IS with Seller supplying the CO and Water test and 1 year First American Home Warranty for peace of mind. Relocating for work  and can accommodate a quick closing if needed.   Schedule your showing today before this one gets away!
